text: Habeat quoque eadem Ecclesia, et omnes terrae suae, soccam and saccam, on strond and on streme, on wode and an feld, on grihtbriche, on bourbriche, hundredeseten, adas and ordelas, ealle hordas, bovenerthin, and binechacre infangethef and flemenge ferthe, hamsokene, frihidbriche, forsteal, tol and team.
